io.jenetics.jpx

Class Metadata.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.jenetics.jpx.Metadata.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    Metadata

    public static final class Metadata.Builder
extends Object
    Builder class for creating immutable Metadata objects.

    Creating a GPX object with one track-segment and 3 track-points: 

    
 final Metadata gpx = Metadata.builder()
     .author("Franz Wilhelmst√∂tter")
     .addLink(Link.of("http://jenetics.io"))
     .build();
